Duoduo, what are you doing here?

34
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:25,620
Don't be mad.

35
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:27,460
Uncle Li didn't mean it that way.

36
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:29,020
Then what did he mean?

37
00:02:29,580 --> 00:02:31,180
You heard what he said just now.

38
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:33,180
Tell me, Shao Nian.

39
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,860
If you were me, wouldn't you be mad?

40
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:39,020
I'd be mad too.

41
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:40,900
But Uncle Li is your father.

42
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,140
You know him better than anyone.

43
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,980
His bark is worse than his bite.

44
00:02:44,140 --> 00:02:45,420
You see him

45
00:02:45,420 --> 00:02:46,480
