So much food.

77
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,220
- So much food.
- Thank you.

78
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:44,060
- Gao is here.
- Gao.

79
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,300
Gao Ge.

80
