154
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:16,540
Alright, alright.

155
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:18,100
- I'll take her upstairs.
- I'm still playing.

156
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,580
What are you doing? Today, I'll...

157
