- Let go of me.

160
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,220
Rest early, Duoduo.

161
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,060
Drink less.

162
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,260
Alright, Uncle Li.

163
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,620
Let go of me, Dad.

164
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:28,700
