- Goodbye.

187
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:56,140
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

188
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:57,060
Let us know when you get home.

189
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,180
Okay, got it.

190
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,030
We're leaving now.

191
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,980
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

192
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:06,860
Li Dafu.

193
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:10,420
- You're still up?
- Li Dafu.

194
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:12,620
What's that noise?

195
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:20,740
Li Dafu.

196
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,860
Open the door.

197
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:25,380
