198
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:42,460
Li Dafu.

199
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:46,940
Li Dafu, come out.

200
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:48,280
- Duoduo.
- Li Dafu.

201
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,180
Come out. I want to talk to you.

202
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,020
Duoduo, you're drunk.

203
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:51,250
