00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:23,820
the São Paulo University immediately.

561
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:25,820
From now on,

562
00:23:26,700 --> 00:23:27,740
our school's honor

563
00:23:28,700 --> 00:23:29,780
is in your hands.

564
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:32,210
Great! Thank you, Secretary Zhou.

565
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,340
But

566
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:34,780
I have one condition.

567
00:23:36,540 --> 00:23:37,660
Chen Weilan must play

568
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:40,260
and represent Xingang University in the match.

569
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,420
Since she's a prodigy,

570
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:44,260
she should bring glory to the school.

571
00:23:44,500 --> 00:23:45,500
Don't worry, Secretary Zhou.

572
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:47,740
Beach volleyball is a two-player sport.

573
00:23:48,420 --> 00:23:49,660
Let Chen Weilan

574
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:51,300
choose her own partner.

575
00:23:53,700 --> 00:23:54,740
They need to work well together

576
00:23:55,460 --> 00:23:58,120
to win this friendly match.

577
00:23:58,130 --> 00:23:59,340
Alright, don't worry, Secretary Zhou.

578
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:00,970
You can do this.

579
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:02,020
- We can do this.
- We can do this.

580
00:24:18,780 --> 00:24:19,940
Why are you here alone?

581
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:23,860
I'm worried about Chen Weilan.

582
00:24:24,380 --> 00:24:25,220
What's wrong with her?

583
00:24:26,460 --> 00:24:27,740
Today, Secretary Zhou requested her

584
00:24:27,740 --> 00:24:29,500
to represent Xingang in the friendly match.

585
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:31,580
I'm not sure if she can handle it.

586
00:24:31,580 --> 00:24:32,420
Just because of that?

587
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,740
Her wrist is injured.

588
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:36,980
If her wrist injury flares up,

589
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:39,020
I don't know if she could make it.

590
00:24:41,060 --> 00:24:42,620
No need to worry so much about it.

591
00:24:43,180 --> 00:24:44,860
Chen Weilan has a lot of experience in sports.

592
00:24:45,420 --> 00:24:47,260
If her wrist injury was serious,

593
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:48,700
she would have told us long ago.

594
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,260
She wouldn't risk her career

595
00:24:50,260 --> 00:24:51,780
over one match.

596
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:56,580
I hope so.

597
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:57,860
Secretary Zhou said

598
00:24:58,180 --> 00:25:00,500
Chen Weilan has to play

599
00:25:00,700 --> 00:25:01,740
against São Paulo University.

600
00:25:02,990 --> 00:25:03,850
Of course.

601
00:25:03,860 --> 00:25:05,220
It has to be the best player.

602
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:07,780
Who will play with me?

603
00:25:08,060 --> 00:25:09,380
That's what we need

604
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:10,300
to discuss today.

605
00:25:11,300 --> 00:25:12,140
Secretary Zhou said

606
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,300
you should choose your own partner

607
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,340
since you know best

608
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:16,460
what kind of partner you need.

609
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,940
I get to choose?

610
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:30,620
Me! Pick me!

611
00:25:31,860 --> 00:25:32,700
Her.

612
00:25:36,300 --> 00:25:37,700
Why Wen Xin?

613
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:39,500
We both play indoor volleyball,

614
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:41,140
so we should be able

615
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:42,580
to work together better.

616
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:44,260
But neither of you has played beach volleyball.

617
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:47,260
Isn't it easy to transition

618
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,620
from indoor to beach volleyball?

619
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:51,260
Plus, we still have some time before the match.

620
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:52,100
We can train for it.

621
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:53,500
Can you get used to the sand?

622
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,100
- No problem.
- Okay.

623
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,420
Do we need to tell Secretary Zhou?

624
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,900
No, I'll let him know.

625
00:26:00,140 --> 00:26:01,460
- Okay.
- So it's settled.

626
00:26:01,700 --> 00:26:03,220
You all can discuss freely now.

627
00:26:04,260 --> 00:26:05,100
Weilan.

628
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,740
- Duoduo.
- Today...

629
00:26:10,580 --> 00:26:11,700
She just wants to win

630
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:12,820
this friendly match.

631
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:15,050
We two can work together.

632
00:26:15,050 --> 00:26:16,250
- I know.
- It should be good, right?

633
00:26:19,700 --> 00:26:20,620
Weilan,

634
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:21,620
why don't the two of us

635
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:22,660
be your sparring partners?

636
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:28,460
Sure.

637
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:29,860
Great.

638
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:33,180
Let's go.

639
00:26:34,220 --> 00:26:35,420
How should we train later?

640
00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:36,260
What should we practice?

641
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:38,540
- Should we start with passing?
- Or bumping?

642
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:40,500
Wait a minute.

643
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:45,260
What's up, Duoduo?

644
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:48,220
Duoduo.

645
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,380
What's going on?

646
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:51,140
During practice,

647
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:52,380
follow my instructions.

648
00:26:52,780 --> 00:26:53,620
Wen Xin,

649
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:55,380
you'll handle the reception

650
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:56,740
and spiking.

651
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:58,420
Jing Xuan, when you spike,

652
00:26:58,420 --> 00:26:59,820
try to aim towards Wen Xin.

653
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:03,380
Why?

654
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,220
Chen Weilan is quite skilled.

655
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:07,820
Though she may not be used to the sand now,

656
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:09,100
with her skills,

657
00:27:09,100 --> 00:27:10,300
she'll adapt quickly.

658
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:13,380
Just do as I say,

659
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:14,220
okay?

660
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,260
But Duoduo,

661
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:16,780
if you don't explain,

662
00:27:16,980 --> 00:27:18,500
it's hard for us to follow.

663
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:19,780
Duoduo,

664
00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:21,900
you're her roommate.

665
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:23,460
Do you know something?

666
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:25,980
She has an injury on her hand.

667
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:27,820
She's injured?

668
00:27:28,100 --> 00:27:29,620
Ask her to go to the hospital right away.

669
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,020
I thought the same,

670
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,340
but she's so strong-willed.

671
00:27:32,340 --> 00:27:33,560
She wouldn't want others to know.

672
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:35,980
So, keep this a secret

673
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:36,940
and don't tell anyone else.

674
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:39,980
I understand your point.

675
00:27:40,500 --> 00:27:41,340
Don't worry.

676
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:43,580
- Don't worry.
- Okay, thanks.

677
00:27:43,900 --> 00:27:44,740
Let's go.

678
00:28:04,060 --> 00:28:05,100
I don't get it.

679
00:28:05,100 --> 00:28:06,860
What's up with you three today?

680
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:09,100
Why are we practicing passing all the time?

681
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:12,460
We're just trying to improve our passing

682
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:13,840
- before moving on to other things.
- Yes.

683
00:28:14,860 --> 00:28:16,380
I can't pass well,

684
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,980
so I want to practice more with you.

685
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:19,340
Yes, Chen Weilan.

686
00:28:19,940 --> 00:28:21,340
Passing is important in beach volleyball.

687
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:22,740
If the setting isn't good,

688
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,780
it's hard to spike.

689
00:28:25,060 --> 00:28:26,460
Isn't spiking important?

690
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,940
Which one can score, passes or spikes?

691
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:31,020
If you want to keep practicing passes,

692
00:28:31,020 --> 00:28:33,020
you can do it. I'm going to practice spiking.

693
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:35,460
We're not saying you can't practice spiking.

694
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:37,100
You just can't practice spiking for a while.

695
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:37,980
Do it later.

696
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,220
What?

697
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:41,900
Why can't I

698
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:42,820
practice spiking now?

699
00:28:44,340 --> 00:28:45,780
As a professional athlete,

700
00:28:45,780 --> 00:28:47,060
you should do something professional.

701
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:50,340
I don't understand what you're saying.

702
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:52,700
What does spiking have to do

703
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:53,580
with being professional?

704
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:56,580
If you were professional,
you wouldn't train with an injury.

705
00:28:56,620 --> 00:28:57,460
Duoduo.

706
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:00,740
You told them, didn't you?

707
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:03,900
You all know, don't you?

708
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:08,460
You didn't need to share my business
with everyone.

709
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,460
I'm perfectly fine.

710
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:13,260
Weilan...

711
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:45,060
(Guoguo Duoduo)

712
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:05,020
(Dafu BBQ)

713
00:30:05,020 --> 00:30:06,260
- Sir.
- Your skewers.

714
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:08,140
Thank you.

715
00:30:11,980 --> 00:30:13,220
Please wait a moment.

716
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:14,300
Okay.

717
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,060
It smells so good today.

718
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:18,500
It's always like this.

719
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,580
Duoduo.

720
00:30:23,340 --> 00:30:25,180
How's training been? Is it tiring?

721
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:28,100
The team is being disbanded.

722
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:29,580
The match is canceled too.

723
00:30:30,420 --> 00:30:31,260
Why?

724
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:04,860
Are you still angry?

725
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:25,860
I didn't mean

726
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:28,980
to look at your injury report.

727
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:30,900
I saw it by accident.

728
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:32,780
But you saw it.

729
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:34,460
Why did you have to tell everyone?

730
00:31:34,980 --> 00:31:37,420
I was worried

731
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:39,820
that if we didn't work well together

732
00:31:39,820 --> 00:31:41,300
during training,

733
00:31:41,860 --> 00:31:42,820
your condition might worsen.

734
00:31:42,820 --> 00:31:44,620
This is my privacy.

735
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:47,100
Didn't I tell you not to meddle?

736
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:52,100
But we're on the same team now.

737
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:53,260
We're teammates.

738
00:31:53,580 --> 00:31:55,340
I have an obligation to help you.

739
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:57,640
If you're injured,
I have a duty to help you heal.

740
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,260
Besides,

741
00:31:59,580 --> 00:32:01,740
it's not shameful for an athlete
to get injured.

742
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,460
Many athletes get injured.

743
00:32:03,460 --> 00:32:04,860
It's unavoidable.

744
00:32:05,900 --> 00:32:08,020
Injuries should be treated promptly,

745
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:09,860
so you can perform better

746
00:32:09,860 --> 00:32:11,420
in training and matches.

747
00:32:13,260 --> 00:32:15,060
Is that the reason you told everyone?

748
00:32:15,580 --> 00:32:16,740
To make them pity me?

749
00:32:18,420 --> 00:32:19,500
Pity?

750
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:22,100
This isn't about pity.

751
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:23,540
This is for your own good.

752
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,580
We're all trying to help you heal.

753
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:26,540
We want to help you.

754
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:27,700
Li Guoduo,

755
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:29,540
I don't need that kind of help.

756
00:32:31,540 --> 00:32:33,300
I know my own issues.

757
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,860
If you all keep playing like today,

758
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:36,180
going easy on me during training,

759
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,100
I don't see any reason

760
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:39,340
to stay on this team.

761
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:56,700
That's all.

762
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,100
Chen Weilan feels

763
00:32:58,300 --> 00:32:59,700
her pride is hurt

764
00:32:59,900 --> 00:33:00,980
and doesn't want to stay on the team.

765
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,460
What should I do?

766
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:06,900
I don't think that's possible.

767
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:08,940
Chen Weilan loves volleyball so much.

768
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:10,260
How could she just quit?

769
00:33:10,740 --> 00:33:12,220
She's been training secretly every day.

770
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:13,060
Saying she won't play now

771
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:13,980
doesn't make sense.

772
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:16,100
She just said that in the heat of the moment.

773
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:17,540
Really?

774
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,540
It must be. Think about it.

775
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,380
Shao Nian.

776
00:33:20,220 --> 00:33:21,500
- Coming.
- Serve the food.

777
00:33:21,500 --> 00:33:22,860
Don't worry. I'll help you out.

778
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:25,540
Coming.

779
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:32,860
- That table.
- That table, right?

780
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:33,700
Okay.

781
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:36,860
Here you go.

782
00:33:36,860 --> 00:33:37,700
This is the rest.

783
00:33:38,420 --> 00:33:39,500
Okay, thanks.

784
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:04,300
Your wrist is fine, right?

785
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,300
Duoduo was worried you'd quit the team

786
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,620
and worried all night.

787
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:13,180
I never planned to quit the team,

788
00:34:14,180 --> 00:34:15,580
but I also don't plan to forgive her.

789
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:18,180
Duoduo was wrong in this.

790
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,860
She even considered moving out of the dorm

791
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:21,180
to make it up to you.

792
00:34:25,340 --> 00:34:26,700
Is it really that serious?

793
00:34:27,460 --> 00:34:28,700
Move out?

794
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:29,740
Come on.

795
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:31,700
How childish.

796
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,540
Duoduo has always been like this.

797
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:35,940
You know her.

798
00:34:36,300 --> 00:34:37,740
She's a bit clumsy.

799
00:34:37,940 --> 00:34:38,780
Let me tell you.

800
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:41,540
My injury report is from a year ago.

801
00:34:41,940 --> 00:34:43,340
Not only is she clumsy,

802
00:34:43,740 --> 00:34:44,900
but her eyes aren't great either.

803
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,660
Your wrist injury

804
00:34:47,660 --> 00:34:48,820
was from a year ago?

805
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,140
Duoduo thought

806
00:34:52,140 --> 00:34:53,540
you were training with an injury

807
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,740
and felt bad for you.

808
00:34:55,340 --> 00:34:56,260
Well, that's settled then.

809
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,660
No need to worry about you quitting the team.

810
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:00,420
I never thought about quitting the team.

811
00:35:00,580 --> 00:35:01,780
She's the one overthinking it.

812
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:03,940
Why is she overthinking it?

813
00:35:04,250 --> 00:35:05,380
Isn't it because she cares about you?

814
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,740
If she didn't care,

815
00:35:06,740 --> 00:35:08,140
she could easily find another partner.

816
00:35:08,140 --> 00:35:09,340
Does she care about me?

817
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:11,420
She cares about having a partner.

818
00:35:14,740 --> 00:35:16,860
Duoduo loves beach volleyball.

819
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,460
From the day I met her,

820
00:35:20,260 --> 00:35:22,180
she's never given up on it.

821
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:23,940
She would do anything for it.

822
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:25,500
Do you know

823
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,620
how worried she was

824
00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:27,940
when she saw your diagnosis?

825
00:35:28,660 --> 00:35:29,400
She was terrified you'd

826
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,640
have to stop playing beach volleyball

827
00:35:30,640 --> 00:35:31,900
because of your injury.

828
00:35:33,130 --> 00:35:35,020
She knows you're like her.

829
00:36:12,340 --> 00:36:13,180
It's fine.

830
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:14,020
Okay.

831
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:14,860
Take a break.

832
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:29,860
Duoduo,

833
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,580
you saved the ball beautifully today.

834
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:34,020
If only I could spike

835
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:35,460
as powerfully as Weilan.

836
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,620
I've been practicing for so long

837
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:38,660
but still can't get it right.

838
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:40,500
If I had finished those spikes,

839
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:42,020
we wouldn't have lost so many points.

840
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:43,220
Take your time.

841
00:36:43,420 --> 00:36:45,180
She's been professionally trained
for a long time.

842
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:48,140
And your defense and passing are already great.

843
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:52,020
If my spikes were stronger,

844
00:36:52,220 --> 00:36:53,820
I could become a versatile player.

845
00:36:56,060 --> 00:36:56,900
I need to practice hard.

846
00:36:58,380 --> 00:36:59,820
You can do it. Keep going!

847
00:37:00,540 --> 00:37:01,380
I can do it.

848
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:05,740
Weilan.

849
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:09,740
What's up?

850
00:37:09,740 --> 00:37:10,980
I wanted to discuss something with you.

851
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:12,700
Go ahead.

852
00:37:13,220 --> 00:37:15,060
We have just joined the beach volleyball team,

853
00:37:15,070 --> 00:37:16,380
and this is our first time partnering.

854
00:37:16,700 --> 00:37:18,580
We have some strong opponents ahead.

855
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:20,420
So...

856
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:23,460
Just say it.

857
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:26,060
So,

858
00:37:26,740 --> 00:37:28,380
I've thought it over

859
00:37:28,580 --> 00:37:30,460
and I might not be the best partner for you.

860
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,380
Someone else might be more suitable.

861
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,700
It doesn't matter who I play with.

862
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:41,100
Even a newcomer is fine.

863
00:37:43,540 --> 00:37:44,820
Are you sure you don't want to reconsider?

864
00:37:45,140 --> 00:37:45,980
It's okay.

865
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:54,580
(São Paulo University VS Xingang University)

866
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:56,260
Hey, everyone!

867
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:58,500
We're at the venue now.

868
00:37:58,700 --> 00:37:59,780
Today's match

869
00:37:59,780 --> 00:38:01,380
will be held here.

870
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:04,330
Intercollegiate matches like this

871
00:38:04,330 --> 00:38:05,690
happen often.

872
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:07,860
Look at today's cheerleaders.

873
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:10,020
