has sent their international team.

876
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:18,300
The two players are back home for this match.

877
00:38:18,620 --> 00:38:20,500
They must be confident too.

878
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:22,340
Let's look forward

879
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:24,820
to an exciting performance from both teams.

880
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:29,020
You guys are so lucky!

881
00:38:30,300 --> 00:38:31,500
They're all so beautiful.

882
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:32,980
Let's take a selfie.

883
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,460
Come on, let's do the pose they want.

884
00:38:34,460 --> 00:38:35,460
Come on, come on!

885
00:38:35,460 --> 00:38:36,460
Stop taking pictures. Hurry up!

886
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:37,300
It's about to start.

887
00:38:38,260 --> 00:38:40,460
Don't shout. Don't shout.

888
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:44,740
What's going on, Liqiang?

889
00:38:44,980 --> 00:38:45,820
Got hit again?

890
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,420
Why are you here alone? Where are the others?

891
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:49,740
Chen Weilan said she was coming
from her grandpa's house.

892
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:51,350
Duoduo and Wen Xin
were coming from the school.

893
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:52,220
They haven't arrived yet?

894
00:38:53,620 --> 00:38:54,460
Nope.

895
00:38:56,850 --> 00:38:57,740
Let's wait a bit longer.

896
00:38:57,740 --> 00:38:58,580
They should be here soon.

897
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:00,020
Okay.

898
00:39:00,420 --> 00:39:01,700
Can the car be fixed?

899
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:04,460
We're running out of time. What do we do?

900
00:39:04,860 --> 00:39:05,740
What should we do?

901
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:07,180
Let's take a cab.

902
00:39:07,820 --> 00:39:09,060
Duoduo, there's a car over there.

903
00:39:09,740 --> 00:39:11,290
Taxi! Taxi!

904
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:12,660
Go, go, go!

905
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,940
- Wen Xin, what's wrong?
- Sorry, sorry.

906
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:18,060
- Sorry, sorry.
- Are you okay?

907
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:19,500
What's wrong with you?

908
00:39:20,060 --> 00:39:20,900
How's your foot?

909
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:22,300
I think I twisted my ankle.

910
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:23,340
Are you okay?

911
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:25,820
Let me take you to the hospital.

912
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:26,780
Okay, let's go.

913
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:29,900
No, no, no.

914
00:39:29,900 --> 00:39:30,900
It hurts a lot.

915
00:39:31,540 --> 00:39:33,260
How did it get so bad?

916
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:38,380
Hello, Shao Nian?

917
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:40,140
How's it going? Have you reached the venue?

918
00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:42,260
We have a bit of an emergency here.

919
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:43,980
Wen Xin twisted her ankle.

920
00:39:44,540 --> 00:39:46,380
Okay, send me your location.
I'll come to find you.

921
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:47,460
Alright, I'll send it right now.

922
00:39:47,460 --> 00:39:48,700
Hurry over, please.

923
00:39:59,500 --> 00:40:00,340
What time is it?

924
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:01,940
It's almost time.

925
00:40:09,780 --> 00:40:11,060
Is it still hurting?

926
00:40:11,170 --> 00:40:12,020
It's much better now.

927
00:40:12,020 --> 00:40:12,860
Alright, alright.

928
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:13,980
Is the bone okay?

929
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:15,820
I've already told her.

930
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:16,660
She's on her way now.

931
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:17,540
You should go too.

932
00:40:17,740 --> 00:40:18,900
Okay, then Wen Xin...

933
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:19,880
I'll take her to the infirmary.

934
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,660
Don't worry about me.

935
00:40:21,660 --> 00:40:23,100
It's just a minor injury.

936
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:25,820
Focus on the match.

937
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:27,740
Xingang University's reputation

938
00:40:27,740 --> 00:40:28,620
is on your shoulders.

939
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:30,820
- Go for it.
- Sure.

940
00:40:39,100 --> 00:40:40,420
- Thank you.
- Don't mention it.

941
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:42,780
Hurry to the venue.

942
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:44,580
I'll rest a bit and head back on my own.

943
