There's no one around now.

944
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:48,620
Be honest with me.

945
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:50,580
Why are you pretending to be injured?

946
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:53,500
This

947
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:55,060
is a real injury.

948
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:56,740
When I treated your sprain today,

949
00:40:56,740 --> 00:40:58,620
I realized you could actually play.

950
00:40:59,740 --> 00:41:00,980
But I didn't expose you

951
00:41:02,050 --> 00:41:03,580
because I didn't want
to hurt Duoduo's feelings.

952
00:41:05,100 --> 00:41:06,380
Duoduo has been abandoned once

953
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:08,020
in a match.

954
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:10,460
I don't want her to be abandoned a second time.

955
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:18,020
You misunderstood.

956
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:20,060
I never intended to abandon her.

957
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,780
I've long noticed

958
00:41:23,180 --> 00:41:24,580
Weilan excels at offense.

959
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:26,380
Spiking is her specialty.

960
00:41:27,060 --> 00:41:28,100
And Duoduo,

961
00:41:28,260 --> 00:41:29,220
with her quick reflexes,

962
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:31,100
is excellent at defense.

963
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:32,380
Think about it.

964
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,260
One is the strongest spear.

965
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:36,740
The other is the sturdiest shield.

966
00:41:37,340 --> 00:41:40,060
I think they're the perfect pair.

967
00:41:42,900 --> 00:41:43,780
But before today,

968
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:45,140
I never knew

969
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,620
how to let them

970
00:41:46,620 --> 00:41:47,980
team up.

971
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:51,540
Then I accidentally fell today,

972
00:41:51,820 --> 00:41:53,380
and that gave me this idea.

973
00:41:57,020 --> 00:41:57,860
Do you really think

974
00:41:57,860 --> 00:41:59,020
they make a good team?

975
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:02,980
As long as they work well together,

976
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:04,580
today's match will be fine.

977
00:42:06,420 --> 00:42:07,980
Alright, you should get to the venue.

978
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,500
I'll head back soon.

979
00:42:10,300 --> 00:42:11,620
Are you okay managing your injury alone?

980
00:42:12,540 --> 00:42:14,340
Go. Don't miss the match.

981
00:42:14,580 --> 00:42:15,900
Alright, I'll go now.

982
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,900
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

983
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:28,620
I'm here. I'm here!

984
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:30,620
How's Wen Xin's foot?

985
00:42:30,620 --> 00:42:31,300
Wenxin is fine.

986
00:42:31,300 --> 00:42:32,540
Shao Nian has taken her to the hospital.

987
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:33,500
It should be nothing serious.

988
00:42:33,500 --> 00:42:34,780
Hospital?

989
00:42:35,540 --> 00:42:36,540
What do we do now?

990
00:42:36,780 --> 00:42:37,780
The match is about to start.

991
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:39,780
I'll take her place.

992
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,300
But we haven't played together even once.

993
00:42:43,300 --> 00:42:44,140
Are you sure?

994
00:42:44,140 --> 00:42:45,420
I'm sure. Don't worry.

995
00:42:45,420 --> 00:42:46,580
I'll play my best.

996
00:42:48,260 --> 00:42:49,340
Okay then.

997
00:42:49,340 --> 00:42:50,180
That's all we can do.

998
00:42:50,460 --> 00:42:51,300
Hurry and change.

999
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:52,660
Okay, I'll do my best.

1000
00:42:52,900 --> 00:42:54,140
I can do this. I can do this.

1001
00:42:54,140 --> 00:42:55,460
- Make sure to coordinate.
- Okay.

1002
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,340
Are you sure?

1003
